Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.72,0:01:32.52,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,First base! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.65,0:01:34.61,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Second base! Yay!
