Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:32.46,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,A cellphone decoration? You're really dexterous with your fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.46,0:02:38.17,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,You could say that. I might not look it, but I'm rather crafty with my hands.{repeat of the phrase above, but changed the wording. minorin's crafty with her fingers (since she decorates phones)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.17,0:02:41.01,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What's Kushieda doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:46.43,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,All right, one down!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.35,0:02:51.52,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Next up is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.11,0:02:57.11,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that smothered voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:02:59.36,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Um, y-you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.36,0:03:02.66,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why don't I decorate yours too, Takasu-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.70,0:03:07.20,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,You see, I'm a part-time cellphone decorator.{artisan or craftsman, whichever works for someone who does artsy shit to decorate stuff}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:08.83,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,D-Decorator?{same as above}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.83,0:03:12.08,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,I'll spell out "Ryuuji" with purple Swarovski stones on yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:15.59,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFawn Script\fad(300,0)\frz354.686\bord1\3c&H7F274D&\c&HDFA7B3&\move(360,157,364,139)}Ryuuji
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:16.50,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,She'd do that for me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:20.22,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,No, {\alpha&HFF&}I-I'm all rig...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.22,0:03:21.38,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,No, I-I'm all rig...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:23.09,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:24.26,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Please decorate ours, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.26,0:03:26.60,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,I see, more orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.89,0:03:33.31,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,On this paper, write down your name, the color you want, and a small drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:38.73,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,To give it a lovely feeling, I'll go with a large heart and the color pink.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:39.82,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}That's lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.57,0:03:46.62,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,So she's a part-time cellphone decorator...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.58,0:03:53.96,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,The sparkling Kushieda and her sparkling\Ndecorations. What a wonderful combination.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:04:01.09,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,100)}Hey, Yacchan's not eating here since she's at the hostess club, right? Then can I have her side dish...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:04.84,Alt,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,And she said "Ryuuji." She remembered my first name...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.01,0:04:08.05,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,That's because I address you like that all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.05,0:04:10.27,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,But anyway, about Yacchan's side dish...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:11.93,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh man, I talked with her so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:15.06,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga, was I able to talk normally with...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.60,0:04:16.40,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,...her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.36,0:04:21.94,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Listen when people are talking to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.49,0:04:26.99,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,And no, you sounded really shady!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.45,0:04:29.37,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What about dinner, is it ready yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:31.95,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt, you know! It's almost done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:35.33,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Today, we're having a rice bowl dish, so as long as we have rice we'll be ok-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:36.71,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What the?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:37.83,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:42.46,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,The rice cooker's broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:46.72,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome and good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:50.51,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What should I get?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.76,0:04:53.02,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Going all the way out to a family restaurant...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:56.19,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't have any rice, but there was bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.19,0:04:58.52,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Bay while you can, mongrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:05:01.69,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Soon, you'll be kneeling your head in gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.86,0:05:05.90,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,And here you go, two servings!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.90,0:05:08.95,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But we haven't ordered anyth-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.53,0:05:10.37,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.24,0:05:16.04,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Keep this a secret. An extra large serving of ice cream, the Taiga Special!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.46,0:05:18.63,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Hide it from the other customers while you eat it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:20.42,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for making it every time, Minorin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:23.51,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,"Every time"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:26.42,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun doesn't like sweet things?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.42,0:05:28.89,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about some french fries?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.89,0:05:32.64,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a huge serving! A {\i1}huge{\i0}  serving!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:34.18,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.39,0:05:39.06,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin also works part time at places like\Nconvenience stores and karaoke clubs, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:42.94,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! And last week, I added a shabu-shabu place to the list!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:44.23,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,That many?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:46.40,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm still saving time for other things!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:51.66,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Being the girls' softball club's captain, I can't possibly skip club activities, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:55.16,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Are you working so hard because you want something in particular?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:58.58,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I've just got the time so I gotta labor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:05:59.87,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,"Labor"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.87,0:06:02.75,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the "Mysterious Files of Labor"!{TL notes time, this is a pun-reference to the '96 show Ginrou Kaiki Files}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.21,0:06:05.46,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,The kind of labor that revives you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:11.72,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,But, wow, you two sure are close now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.39,0:06:17.10,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,Waitress, some cold water, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:18.73,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Well, enjoy your time here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:38.25,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure I've lost some eyesight because you've been poking my eyes all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.25,0:06:42.88,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You pitiful mongrel, drooling while checking out Minorin's uniform...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.29,0:06:45.71,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:50.18,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,...that her smile was so bright...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.30,0:06:54.14,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Sp-Spare my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:06:57.56,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,If I continue, my fingers will be contaminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.02,0:06:59.85,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Damnit...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.14,0:07:04.77,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,But why is she juggling all those jobs?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:07.32,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,She called it the "Mysterious Files of Labor", didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.57,0:07:13.16,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be possible that she has a reason for earning all that money?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.16,0:07:16.74,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Something related to her home? Maybe she's helping her sick mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:18.49,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,She called it laboring.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.70,0:07:20.04,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,But even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:26.46,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You should stop assuming things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:26.97,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.97,0:07:31.26,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm the only one who truly understands her!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:33.13,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It'll only add on to your filth level.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:39.10,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Ew, how gross! Keep your distance from me, you're so disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:44.73,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Taiga! What's with your tone, you're so cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:50.49,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away from me! Since when have I {\i1}not{\i0}  been cold towards you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.49,0:07:51.99,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:58.20,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Inko-chan! Sorry to make you wait, it's dinner time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:04.00,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a huge serving! A {\i1}huge{\i0}  serving!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.75,0:08:06.33,Default,Inko-chan,0000,0000,0000,,-nko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.33,0:08:08.88,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, today you'll be able to say it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:09.84,Default,Inko-chan,0000,0000,0000,,-nko, -oop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.96,0:08:11.80,Default,Inko-chan,0000,0000,0000,,Poop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.81,0:08:30.73,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Man, the mornings during holidays are really refreshing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.19,0:08:28.15,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fnJanieHmkBold\bord1\c&H4E413C&\3c&HA69997&\an7\pos(158,251)\frz347.244}We've gone out for breakfast.\NThere's sandwiches in the fridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.19,0:08:28.15,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\fnJanieHmkBold\bord1\c&H4E413C&\3c&HA69997&\frz5.326\pos(399,308)}Ryuu
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.73,0:08:32.28,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:34.82,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.82,0:08:37.32,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.32,0:08:41.08,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Not bothering to prepare breakfast in order to see Minorin at the family restaurant...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:45.04,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped, the rice cooker is still broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:47.25,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't we go to an electrical appliance store first?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:50.46,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,You even said you hate bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:53.05,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind eating bread for breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.05,0:08:56.84,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so cheerful? Those clothes don't look good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.59,0:08:58.89,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot something at home-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:00.60,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What an annoying idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:02.64,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you, let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.64,0:09:04.98,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What you wear won't make a difference!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:06.48,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.98,0:09:08.98,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you Mirano-chan's son?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:11.19,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, old man Inage?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.48,0:09:14.59,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,"Mirano"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:19.49,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Yasuko's hostess name.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.16,0:09:20.33,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H615DB6&\3c&H0F263D&\pos(255,354)\fs20\fnBeatsville\bord1.2}Mirano-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:21.79,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\an5\fs20\b1\bord0\shad0\be1\fnBeinetCondensed\frx1\fry10\org(367,-481)\frz5.714\pos(368,166)}Vaisravana's\NHeaven
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:21.79,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\an5\fs20\b1\bord0\shad0\be1\fnBeinetCondensed\frx1\fry10\org(367,-481)\frz5.714\pos(368,166)\1a&HFF&\t(0,500,\1a&H50&)}Vaisravana's\NHeaven
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.99,0:09:27.46,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Hi! Go out the station's north exit, it's 200 meters straight ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:30.17,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Vaisravana's Heaven's Mirano-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.59,0:09:33.55,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,How old do I look? Twenty-three?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:34.92,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.67,0:09:39.05,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,This is a fortunate morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.43,0:09:43.64,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,And now to grab a feel of Mirano-chan's DNA!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.64,0:09:47.85,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,Nice and firm, being young must be nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.98,0:09:50.10,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.10,0:09:52.90,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, this old guy's pissing me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.61,0:09:57.11,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there, you two! If you haven't eaten breakfast yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:10:00.99,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,I recommend the docosahexaenoic acid and the calcium-filled taste of this Gyonisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:02.08,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.08,0:10:03.24,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:08.04,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.37,0:10:09.58,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:13.67,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HE5EFDF&\3c&H6A8449&\fnBeinetCondensed\b1\frx14\fry348\frz1.078\pos(410,310)}INAGE LIQUOR STORE
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.25,0:10:13.67,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,Here, carry this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.30,0:10:16.46,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.46,0:10:17.59,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,Another!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:19.68,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,And some more!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.18,0:10:24.93,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,It would be better if I-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.93,0:10:29.60,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay. Sit down and relax with some tea. You're Mirano-chan's son, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:34.69,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:38.61,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,I ask her for some help, but only during holidays.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.61,0:10:41.11,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda, you better work hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.11,0:10:43.12,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:48.58,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,We've run out of workers these days, now that we're so busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:50.08,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,You ran out of workers...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:55.50,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, do you want to work here too, young lady? Being friends with Kushieda and all...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:57.38,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay you well!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.55,0:10:59.26,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.09,0:11:04.35,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'll work!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.56,0:11:06.81,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Along with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.86,0:11:15.44,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I can't keep this up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.36,0:11:19.99,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't cause a ruckus. It'll give Kushieda trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.99,0:11:22.86,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Then help out a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.86,0:11:24.82,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,Little girl, I need you to go do the deliveries!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.20,0:11:27.16,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,Three of those beer cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:30.91,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,With pleasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.08,0:11:36.21,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,And that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:38.42,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.30,0:11:45.76,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.64,0:11:53.48,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:56.48,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,You can't ride a bike?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.69,0:11:59.28,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:05.41,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,So what if I can't ride a bike?! I'll just have to transport it like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:08.16,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,That's wrong! You're doing it wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.66,0:12:10.87,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,You're on fire, Taiga!{literally Minorin's saying that stuff's spurting from Taiga??}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:13.62,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,She's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:18.79,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if she just pushes the bike, she'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:22.21,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right, I was going to restock the shochu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.93,0:12:26.97,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'll-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:29.68,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.35,0:12:34.39,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'd feel bad if I wasn't doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:39.36,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll be counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:45.57,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:58.96,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the potato shochu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.09,0:13:01.50,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,It's really hard to see in this darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.46,0:13:04.34,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,This place isn't used that often.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.92,0:13:07.26,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,They don't open up this place more than once a week or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:11.56,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,If we got locked in here, it'd be horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:14.60,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,It would feel almost like we were stranded or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.35,0:13:21.61,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,That little runt, leaving it open like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.53,0:13:29.95,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! There are still people inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:32.70,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,S.O.S.! S.O.S.!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.45,0:13:35.96,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:37.54,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:40.50,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,It's for these times that we have school songs!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.04,0:13:41.71,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:43.75,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,School songs?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.40,0:14:09.91,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,This is dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.91,0:14:13.62,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason for me to make an effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:16.79,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I really can't keep this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.79,0:14:17.71,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Keep what up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:27.42,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kitamura-kun! W-Why are you h-h-here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.42,0:14:28.92,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Self-training.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.55,0:14:32.39,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, is that your bike?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.93,0:14:39.27,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Um, yeah... something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:43.52,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,You're capable of riding a bike now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.52,0:14:45.40,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,That's remarkable progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.44,0:14:50.20,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Um, putting aside whether I can ride a bike or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:57.24,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know that I didn't know how to ride a bike?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:15:02.37,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,That's because I was closely observing you last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:07.84,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Bikes are great. The world opens up before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.38,0:15:12.76,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.27,0:15:22.60,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,He was observing me last year...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:33.03,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Damnit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.37,0:15:41.41,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Damnit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.79,0:15:46.17,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Opening up a world in which\NKitamura-kun's not watching me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:55.26,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,...is meaningless!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.64,0:16:00.77,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,Two, thr-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:07.19,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you lat- What happened, you look awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.19,0:16:10.03,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing much. Where are the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.19,0:16:14.07,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right, where has that Kushieda run off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:16.74,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,Not minding Ryuuji-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:22.54,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,That mongrel, slacking off in comfort while I'm out working!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.70,0:16:24.37,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,What're you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.37,0:16:26.33,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, the next delivery's three blocks away-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.63,0:16:32.30,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji, what the hell are you up to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.38,0:16:40.97,Default,Ryuuji & Minori,0000,0000,0000,,♪ The bridge that leads to the future ♫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.97,0:16:44.81,Default,Ryuuji & Minori,0000,0000,0000,,♫ That bridge is a chopstick, a chopstick ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:47.81,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,My throat's all dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.81,0:16:51.15,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody noticed us even though we raised our voices...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:54.86,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Around this time, the old guy's obsessing over horse racing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.86,0:16:56.20,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.20,0:16:58.45,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,It's gotten a bit cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:17:00.20,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lend you my coat, the-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.20,0:17:02.33,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's warm up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:08.79,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,The pitcher is scared! Hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:12.50,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,The pitcher is scared! Hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.42,0:17:14.92,Alt,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Who's scared? Aren't you the pitcher?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.50,0:17:14.42,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,He's scared! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.42,0:17:16.43,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,He's scared! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.43,0:17:19.97,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,The pitcher is scared! Hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.97,0:17:23.77,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,The pitcher is scared! Hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.56,0:17:25.10,Alt,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you're actually scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.81,0:17:28.44,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Your hand's trembling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:32.73,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it all wrong, I'm trembling from excitement!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.73,0:17:33.98,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go, you'd better be ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.32,0:17:40.78,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.78,0:17:41.87,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Changeover.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:43.45,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,We swap places now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.45,0:17:45.54,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:50.71,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,You see, there's no point being afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.04,0:17:52.79,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.50,0:17:56.17,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,I only need to beat up my weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.05,0:17:58.09,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:01.39,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.89,0:18:03.10,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.76,0:18:08.19,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takasu-kun. Can't we get out through that window?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.10,0:18:15.82,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he?! Where is he?! Where is he?! Where is he?! Where is he?! Where is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:18.40,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,WHERE IS HE?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.11,0:18:20.70,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Takasu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:24.66,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,So you're in there...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.66,0:18:34.80,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,There might be more to Kushieda's cheerfulness than her simply being bright and energetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.42,0:18:39.01,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:41.84,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Kushieda! Are you oka-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.84,0:18:43.85,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, your nose is bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.51,0:18:47.18,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it'll be okay somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.18,0:18:48.77,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.14,0:18:50.98,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,A nosebleed is the perspiration of your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.65,0:18:54.02,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,That aside, we're almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.02,0:18:55.65,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Keep stacking them boxes, Takasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.65,0:18:56.65,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.69,0:19:01.99,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I see, she was beating up her weakness, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.28,0:19:06.20,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to get out of here!{literally, he's using a baseball term for returning to your home base, which also can be used for surviving in a jungle and return home from like, uh, a planecrash. being liberal.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:09.16,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, of course! Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.16,0:19:09.91,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.91,0:19:12.04,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,When I say fight, you say...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:13.50,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,O-one more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:14.88,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah yeah, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:16.46,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.46,0:19:18.63,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,O-one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:20.63,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.51,0:19:24.14,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,she's always been gleaming with cheerfulness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.22,0:19:26.39,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Even when I had just met her too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.93,0:19:28.52,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.64,0:19:29.60,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Even now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.60,0:19:31.77,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:36.94,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,She's gleaming with joy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.73,0:19:40.57,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,FOU{\alpha&HFF&}ND YOU!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.57,0:19:41.36,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,FOUND {\alpha&HFF&}YOU!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:42.15,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,FOUND YO{\alpha&HFF&}U!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.15,0:19:44.28,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,FOUND YOU!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:58.92,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga, how did you get in here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.96,0:20:02.22,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,How? I used the ladder.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.22,0:20:05.84,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! We can get outside now, Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.22,0:20:06.80,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.80,0:20:08.22,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.22,0:20:10.43,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,This is truly the ladder to the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.43,0:20:11.56,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Minorin...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:13.39,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,You get up too, Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.39,0:20:14.39,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.39,0:20:15.98,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Like I've been trying to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.94,0:20:21.19,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,The ladder fell down when I landed on Ryuuji's face...
